Definition: based on the principle of proportional representation
Example: voters choose between party lists, the number elected from each list being determined by the percentage cast for each list out of the total vote
Synonyms: scrutin_de_liste, scrutin_de_liste_system, voting_system, based, on, the, principle, of, proportional, representation, voters, choose, between, party, lists, number, elected, from, each, list, being, determined, by, percentage, cast, for, out, total, vote
Category: noun.cognition
